org.zodiark.service.broadcaster

Class BroadcastServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zodiark.service.broadcaster.BroadcastServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BroadcasterService, Service

    @On(value={"/chat","/broadcaster"})
public class BroadcastServiceImpl
extends Object
implements BroadcasterService
    Create Broadcaster, or channel, used by PublisherEndpoint and SubscriberEndpoint to communicate.

    A call to the database is always executed in order to retrieve the session information like banned words, etc.
